summary: All runners should do bodybuilding, here's why
title: All runners should do bodybuilding, here's why
body:
All runners should do bodybuilding, here’s why #fitness #runners #bodybuilding #women #Men #world #sport #sports #USA #New

Bodybuilding is the enemy of many endurance athletes! Yet, science is unanimous: adding weight training to your workout program can improve performance. Let’s see how.

In endurance sports, the main determinants of performance are:

  • VO2max, the maximum oxygen consumption by the body;
  • the mechanical efficiency, that is to say what it costs you in energy to move at a certain speed,…

Environ 40 cours collectifs fitness avec coachs certifiés, ainsi que des cours aquabike, aquagym/zumba sont également disponible dans vos centre Lifeclub. Et surtout, sans engagement !
